Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.11,0:00:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}西凉军的精锐主要是他的战骑
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.32,0:00:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这十多万战骑
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.22,0:00:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}分统在李郭二将手中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.72,0:00:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}分别叫龙骧营 虎贲营
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.63,0:00:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}报
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.43,0:00:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}报
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.70,0:00:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}禀盟主
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.50,0:00:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}俞将军与华雄征战一个回合
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.40,0:00:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就被斩落马下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.51,0:00:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}华雄果然英勇啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.81,0:00:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}谁敢出战华雄
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.12,0:01:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}袁公 我有上将军潘凤
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.23,0:01:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}手执一柄百斤重的开山斧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.93,0:01:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}有万夫不挡之勇
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.63,0:01:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}此人必可斩杀华雄
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.10,0:01:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}潘将军何在
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.00,0:01:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}末将在
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.20,0:01:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你敢出战吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.91,0:01:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}有何不敢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.91,0:01:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我的大斧早就饥渴难奈了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.81,0:01:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好 如果你把华雄斩于马下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.71,0:01:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}赏金百两 赐良马五十匹
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.22,0:01:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}领命
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.22,0:01:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}取酒来 为潘将军壮行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.83,0:02:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}如欲攻取洛阳
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.93,0:02:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}必须先破虎牢关 汜水关
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.13,0:03:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我十八镇诸侯可分五路人马进军
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.71,0:03:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}袁盟主可引一路攻取孟津
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.61,0:03:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}孙文台将军可引一路攻取成皋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.42,0:03:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}公孙将军可引一路攻取太谷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.72,0:03:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}祸事了 祸事了 祸事了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.42,0:03:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}禀盟主
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.33,0:03:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}潘将军与华雄征战不到一个回合
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.33,0:03:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就被斩于马下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.23,0:03:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}什么 又被斩了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.33,0:03:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}西凉军果然名不虚传哪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.24,0:03:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}董卓不好对付啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.04,0:03:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}一个小小的华雄都如此棘手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.01,0:03:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}以后碰到吕布该怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.12,0:03:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}谁敢出战华雄
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.62,0:03:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}赏金千两 赠良马百匹
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.43,0:03:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}谁敢出战
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.31,0:04:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}只可惜我的上将颜良 文丑未在
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.72,0:04:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}如有一人在此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.72,0:04:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}岂容华雄放肆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.23,0:04:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}马弓手关羽请战华雄
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.13,0:04:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}什么 你一个小小的弓手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.74,0:04:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}竟敢口出狂言
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.34,0:04:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你以为我们众诸侯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.54,0:04:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}没有大将军了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.44,0:04:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}叉出去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.41,0:04:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}公路兄 息怒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.41,0:04:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.82,0:04:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}此人既敢于请战 必有勇略
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.52,0:04:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}为何不让他试试呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.32,0:05:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}使一个小小的弓手出战
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.63,0:05:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}岂不是让华雄耻笑嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.33,0:05:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}公路兄
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.93,0:05:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}请看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.73,0:05:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}此人生得卧眉凤目 满面英雄气
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.34,0:05:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}华雄又怎么会知道他是个弓手呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.01,0:05:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这个姓曹的说得对
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.01,0:05:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我二哥这个弓手
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.61,0:05:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}胜过你们所有的将军诸侯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.42,0:05:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}若砍不下华雄的头
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.43,0:05:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那就砍关某的头谢罪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.54,0:05:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}刘关张三兄弟义同生死
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.84,0:05:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}如我二弟不胜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.94,0:05:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}愿砍我三兄弟的人头
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.34,0:05:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.52,0:06:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}刘玄德不愧是皇室宗亲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.42,0:06:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}豪气干云
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.92,0:06:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}军校 在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.12,0:06:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}拿酒来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.72,0:06:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我要为这位壮士敬酒壮行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.33,0:06:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}请
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.43,0:06:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不必 小小华雄 何须借酒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.04,0:06:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}诸公稍候 关某去去便回
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.14,0:06:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}二弟小心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.74,0:06:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}哥哥 放心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.69,0:07:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他能行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.53,0:07:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}华雄这么厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.13,0:07:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}估计又是一个人头落地
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.14,0:07:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}马腾将军 你率五千人马策应
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.44,0:07:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这个马弓手如果也死了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.35,0:07:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那又该谁出战哪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.85,0:07:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}西凉军果然名不虚传啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.42,0:07:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}董卓不好对付啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.45,0:08:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.72,0:08:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}赢了 赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.72,0:08:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好 好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.54,0:09:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}听令
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.65,0:09:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}增设第十九镇讨贼兵马
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.55,0:09:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}统兵将军为
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.65,0:10:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}刘备
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.13,0:10:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}刘备领命
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.55,0:10:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}二弟啊 愚兄再敬你一碗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.76,0:10:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你温酒斩华雄 一战成名
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.16,0:10:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}令众路诸侯对咱们兄弟刮目相看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.83,0:10:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就是 就是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.83,0:10:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}二哥 你把华雄的脑袋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.33,0:10:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}往那堂上一扔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.33,0:10:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那满堂的诸侯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.74,0:10:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}全都看傻啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.44,0:10:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}什么刺史啊太守将军的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.74,0:10:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我看哪 都是饭桶草包
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.44,0:10:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}二哥 我也敬你一碗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.45,0:11:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}大哥 关某不负大哥三弟厚望
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.05,0:11:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}侥幸成功 来 来 来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.63,0:11:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}大哥啊 有句话我可先撂下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.53,0:11:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}二哥 你已经是斩将立功了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.13,0:11:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}回头吕布那小子来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.74,0:11:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}可不准二哥你动
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.04,0:11:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}得该轮到我了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.24,0:11:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}成 我让给你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.64,0:11:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}二弟 三弟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.25,0:11:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我们三兄弟此次来会盟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.25,0:11:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}从入关起便饱受其辱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.45,0:11:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}十八路诸侯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.95,0:11:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就根本没把我等放在眼里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.15,0:11:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在这乱世当中
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.86,0:11:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我们要想有立足之地
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.86,0:11:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就必须要靠自己的本事剿贼建功
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.63,0:11:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}方能成就大业
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.03,0:11:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.33,0:11:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你现在也应该是一路诸侯了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.24,0:11:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}第十九镇统兵将军
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.04,0:11:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}如今咱们也可以
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.44,0:11:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}和各路诸侯平起平坐了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.74,0:12:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}未必 我这路将军是虚设的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.25,0:12:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}袁绍袁盟主
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.05,0:12:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}答应给我们的兵马粮饷
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.35,0:12:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}可曾见踪影啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.35,0:12:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我已经派小校去取了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.96,0:12:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}料那袁绍四世三公 名满天下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.43,0:12:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}总不至于言而无信吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.06,0:12:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}再说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.23,0:12:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}二哥 你刚替他斩了华雄立了功
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.43,0:12:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}袁绍那厮如敢赖账
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.24,0:12:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我拿大耳刮子扇他
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.64,0:12:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}主子爷 主子爷 主子爷
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.04,0:12:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}小的叫人给打了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.64,0:12:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}打了 打了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.14,0:12:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他们使大耳刮子打的小的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.15,0:12:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}谁打你 为何打你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.45,0:12:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}小的奉二爷之命
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.75,0:12:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}去大营领取粮饷
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.45,0:12:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}可是那个后将军袁术
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.15,0:12:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他一个子儿也不给咱们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.46,0:12:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你有没有说过
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.96,0:12:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是袁盟主当着众诸侯的面
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.46,0:12:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}许给我们金千斤 马百匹
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.76,0:12:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}粮草五百石
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.76,0:12:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}小的说清楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.43,0:12:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}可袁术说粮草堆在洛阳城呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.04,0:13:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}想要啊 自个打进洛阳城取去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.84,0:13:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}小的和他争辩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.74,0:13:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他的手下就打了小的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.14,0:13:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}还辱骂了三位主公
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.75,0:13:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}骂什么呀 一个字都不准漏
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.05,0:13:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}说给我听听
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.45,0:13:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他们骂 他们骂主子爷是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.05,0:13:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是什么织席贩履之徒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.96,0:13:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}屠猪 屠猪卖狗之徒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.94,0:13:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}奶奶的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.06,0:13:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这帮鸟人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.66,0:13:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}三弟且慢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.96,0:13:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}二哥 你刚替他们出生入死
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.27,0:13:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}斩将立功
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.57,0:13:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这帮鸟人言而无信
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.74,0:13:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}二哥你别管
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.64,0:13:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}让我去捅袁术那小子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.04,0:13:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}一万个透明窟窿
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.04,0:13:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}等等 我们应该和袁绍去说理
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.24,0:13:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}袁绍那小子浑身上下都是嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.15,0:13:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}跟他讲理用口舌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.65,0:13:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}管个鸟用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.75,0:13:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}只能刀下理论
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.05,0:13:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}三弟不可造次
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.16,0:13:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}依我看 无论是说理还是动刀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.23,0:13:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}只怕都没有用
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.06,0:14:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}为何
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.16,0:14:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}袁术是袁绍的堂弟
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.47,0:14:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}而且还是袁绍亲自任命
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.27,0:14:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他为盟军总提调官
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.24,0:14:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我担心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.94,0:14:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}袁术拒不发给我们兵马粮饷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.04,0:14:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}袁绍心里清楚但佯装不知
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.65,0:14:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真没有想到袁氏兄弟名满天下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.55,0:14:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}做起事来竟如此不堪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.85,0:14:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}既然有这层担忧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.65,0:14:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我们干吗还要在这儿寄人篱下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.06,0:14:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在这种地方受这鸟气啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.46,0:14:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我们离开这鸟地方 走人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.46,0:14:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}三弟别急 且听大哥有何主意
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.47,0:14:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.77,0:14:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你们还记得曹操吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.47,0:14:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}当然记得
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.57,0:14:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}此人暗藏韬略 颇有见识
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.24,0:14:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}为人也很仗义
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.94,0:14:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}对我们也算不错
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.95,0:14:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我想不妨先向他请教一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.65,0:14:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}再做定夺
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.95,0:14:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那小子满脸虚情假意
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.75,0:15:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我看也不是什么好东西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.96,0:15:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}禀相国
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.46,0:15:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}上将华雄
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.86,0:15:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}被一个名叫关羽的贼将斩了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.97,0:15:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我三万前军全军溃败
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.17,0:15:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}十八路诸侯共有兵马五十余万
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.87,0:15:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}声势浩大
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.94,0:15:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}前锋将军为长沙太守孙坚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.74,0:15:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他亲率两万精兵 率先进军
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.25,0:15:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}昨日已攻破了白马要寨
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.05,0:15:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}还有 臣刚才得报
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.26,0:15:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}虎牢关也已万急呀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.86,0:15:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}吕布
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.46,0:15:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.36,0:15:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}即刻调集全部西凉人马
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.97,0:15:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}本相要亲自率军出战
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.37,0:15:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.84,0:15:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}相国要亲自率军出战
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.84,0:15:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那定然是马到成功
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.85,0:16:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不过 臣担心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.15,0:16:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}如果相国这次倾城出兵的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.55,0:16:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}城中恐有不虞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.66,0:16:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}把话说明白喽 到底是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.96,0:16:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}相国你是知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.56,0:16:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}现在的朝中大臣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.87,0:16:18.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}大半都是前朝公卿
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.47,0:16:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他们对相国
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.47,0:16:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}对相国你一直是虚与委蛇
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.67,0:16:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}表面恭顺 其心叵测
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.04,0:16:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}比如说袁绍的叔父
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.55,0:16:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}现为朝中太傅的袁隗{\fs14}（隗应读wěi）
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.65,0:16:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}当他得知华雄兵败后
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.85,0:16:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}喜得是手舞足蹈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.15,0:16:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}相国你想一想
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.55,0:16:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}如果你统军倾城出兵 一旦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.06,0:16:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那些大臣们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.86,0:16:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}要是与袁绍里应外合的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.76,0:16:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}则多有不便啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.27,0:16:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}郭汜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.57,0:16:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.67,0:16:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}即刻拿下袁隗全家老少
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.87,0:16:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}明日出征时
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.08,0:17:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}城门下全部斩首祭旗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.28,0:17:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}为我西凉大军壮行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.85,0:17:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}让那些个前朝公卿大臣们看看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.35,0:17:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这就是与我董卓暗中为敌的下场
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.55,0:17:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.56,0:17:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}传令三军
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.76,0:17:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}本相出征后
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.16,0:17:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}五日内要取孙坚首级
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.96,0:17:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}十日内定斩袁绍首级
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.76,0:17:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.97,0:17:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}禀相国 臣还有一个建议
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.07,0:17:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}相国此次剿贼未必一定要力战
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.85,0:17:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}李儒 你把话说明白喽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.85,0:17:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那十八路诸侯中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.55,0:17:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}过去彼此之间一直勾心斗角
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.96,0:17:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}今日又怎么可能同心同德呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.46,0:17:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}相国 你何不使些离间计
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.27,0:18:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}让他们的会盟土崩瓦解
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.56,0:18:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}王允 王司徒大人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.77,0:19:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}本相就要为国剿贼去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.17,0:19:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你就没什么贺辞相赠吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.18,0:19:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}相国歃血出征 威加海内
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.38,0:19:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}臣祝相国马到成功 名留千古
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.86,0:19:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}说得好 说得好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.96,0:19:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}挺会说话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.36,0:19:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}王允哪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.77,0:19:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}看见了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.57,0:19:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这些乱臣的下场
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.37,0:19:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}臣看见了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.68,0:19:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你怕不怕呀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.88,0:19:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}臣怕 怕得浑身发抖
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.28,0:19:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}怕就好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.18,0:19:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你就在城里给我好生的待着
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.95,0:20:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}别给我惹麻烦 听清了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.86,0:20:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}臣遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.76,0:20:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}都听清了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.06,0:20:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}听清了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.87,0:20:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}十日之内 咱家必灭袁绍
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.97,0:20:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}凯旋回京
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.97,0:20:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}到时候
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.37,0:20:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你们就等着喝咱家的庆功酒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.18,0:20:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}斩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.48,0:20:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}将叛贼袁隗满门抄斩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.19,0:20:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}为相国壮行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.06,0:20:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}刀斧手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.96,0:20:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}愿相国出征早日凯旋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.36,0:20:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}饶了袁隗一家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.67,0:20:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我知道你为何要探望刘备他们
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.67,0:20:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}为何啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.07,0:20:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}大哥想把这三人收入摩下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.17,0:20:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}没错 乱世当中
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.58,0:20:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}有的人夺皇权
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.08,0:20:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}有的人抢城池
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.98,0:21:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}有的人抢兵马钱粮
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.98,0:21:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}可是你要记住
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.29,0:21:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}大业之本首在英才
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.79,0:21:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}英才比什么都重要
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.86,0:21:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这三个人可都是英雄啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.63,0:21:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}而且更为难得的是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.26,0:21:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他们现在正处于英雄末路
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.56,0:21:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这种时候你给他们一分好处
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.87,0:21:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}抵得上平时十分
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.17,0:21:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}大哥 这三人虽勇
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.07,0:21:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}却势单力薄啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.97,0:21:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}大哥如想招慕他们
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.37,0:21:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}只需书信一封 黄金百两即可
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.08,0:21:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}何必专程折腰拜访啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.78,0:21:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}无知
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.79,0:21:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}有的人可以召之即来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.49,0:21:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}可是有的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.79,0:21:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你就是千呼万唤他也不一定来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.76,0:21:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这三个人可不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.96,0:21:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你没瞅见他们在帅台上的样子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.27,0:21:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}刘备虽然坐于末座 却器宇轩昂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.87,0:21:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那两个也是 傲视群雄
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.37,0:22:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你知道当关羽把华雄的头颅
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.08,0:22:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}扔到大堂上的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.28,0:22:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我最吃惊的是什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.68,0:22:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是什么呀
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.49,0:22:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是刘备的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.19,0:22:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他连眼皮都没眨一下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.19,0:22:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就好像这一切都是理所当然的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.56,0:22:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这种人 泰山崩于前而面不变色
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.47,0:22:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}深不可测啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.27,0:22:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是啊 我想起来了 的确如此啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.48,0:22:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}大哥 你要是招不动这三个人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.28,0:22:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.98,0:22:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}招不动
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.68,0:22:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那我就让他们主动来投靠我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.39,0:22:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.89,0:22:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}照我看来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.69,0:22:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}大哥你才是天下真正的英主啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.39,0:22:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}刘关张不过是英才而已啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.17,0:23:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在下曹操 拜访刘将军
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.18,0:23:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}原来是曹将军大驾光临
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.38,0:23:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}未及远迎 请恕罪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.29,0:23:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}怎么 这就是第十九镇将军府吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.09,0:23:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}正是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.19,0:23:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好得很
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.49,0:23:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我看它比袁本初的帅台要气派
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.76,0:23:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}曹将军为何这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.47,0:23:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}因为袁绍的帅台虽然显赫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.37,0:23:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}却只围了一群碌碌之徒
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.47,0:23:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}和势利小人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.37,0:23:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这间茅屋
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.67,0:23:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}却住着三个义薄云天的兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.68,0:23:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}风闻
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.98,0:23:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这三个人不求同年同月同日生
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.48,0:23:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但求同年同月同日死
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.29,0:23:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}曹某在百里之外
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.19,0:23:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}都能感到这茅屋里
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.49,0:23:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}所发出的英雄之气啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.19,0:23:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}曹操 你讲得太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.19,0:24:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}刚才我还在骂你来着
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.20,0:24:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}请问翼德老弟刚才骂我什么
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.37,0:24:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我刚才骂你呀虚情假意
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.87,0:24:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}多有得罪了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.97,0:24:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}翼德老弟骂得对
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.48,0:24:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我是宁肯听你骂
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.78,0:24:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}也不愿意听他们的虚情假意
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.88,0:24:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}甜言蜜语
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.78,0:24:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}说得好 说得真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.78,0:24:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}说得我这心里呀舒服死了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.19,0:24:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你知道不
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.79,0:24:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}袁术那哥俩真不是个东西
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.19,0:24:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}三弟
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.80,0:24:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}看来袁绍是食言了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.80,0:24:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}或许袁本初一时疏忽了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.07,0:24:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}三位请看
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.57,0:24:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这车上有千斤粮食 百斤熟肉
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.37,0:24:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}还有十坛美酒
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.68,0:24:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}噢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.58,0:24:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}袁绍把赏赐之物拨发给我们了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.38,0:24:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不是袁绍 是我大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.88,0:24:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我大哥听说袁术
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.38,0:24:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}竟敢难为三位英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.39,0:24:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}立刻令我从我部存粮当中
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.89,0:25:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}拨出一部分来
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.09,0:25:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}相助三位英雄啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.29,0:25:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}拜谢曹将军 多谢
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.00,0:25:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}些许薄物 聊表寸心罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.80,0:25:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不过不是我自夸
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.60,0:25:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这十坛美酒可都是
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.37,0:25:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}沛国的百年佳酿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.57,0:25:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}每一坛都价值百金哪
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.57,0:25:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真的吗 那太好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.38,0:25:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}美酒能让英雄所饮
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.18,0:25:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}也是美酒的福分
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.08,0:25:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}曹仁哪 在
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.48,0:25:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你先陪云长和翼德饮酒
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.79,0:25:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我跟刘将军叙谈片刻 好
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.29,0:25:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.99,0:25:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}走走走走 拿酒
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.09,0:25:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}曹公请入内 请
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.80,0:25:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}请
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.60,0:25:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}京城董贼作乱
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.30,0:25:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}九州战火蜂起
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.27,0:25:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}官民士子
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.27,0:25:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}无不处于水深火热之中啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.48,0:25:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}四百年汉室日渐衰亡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.58,0:26:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我身为刘氏宗人
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.18,0:26:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}何以面对先皇在天之灵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.59,0:26:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}痛哉痛哉
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.69,0:26:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}痛不可当啊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.19,0:26:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我倒是与君不同
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.90,0:26:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}一方面是痛
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.80,0:26:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}另一方面却是喜
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.40,0:26:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}敢问曹公喜从何来
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.61,0:26:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}夏 五百年止于商
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.48,0:26:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}商 五百年止于周
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.88,0:26:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}周 三百年而骤起春秋战国
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.48,0:26:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是时天下大乱
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.29,0:26:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}引来英雄辈出
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.19,0:26:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}由此可见
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.39,0:26:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}国运盛衰长短俱凭天意
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.20,0:26:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}如无乱世 何来英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.30,0:26:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}请君设想 如果是在太平盛世
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.81,0:27:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你只能是个织席贩履之徒
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.98,0:27:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我呢 也只能是个门下校尉之辈
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.68,0:27:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}恰恰是这天下大乱
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.18,0:27:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你我才可能创下不世功名
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.79,0:27:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}看来曹公是为这乱世而生的
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.80,0:27:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}生于乱世是为不幸
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.90,0:27:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但如能变乱为治
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.00,0:27:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}岂非不幸中之大幸
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.71,0:27:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}敢问玄德兄
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.21,0:27:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}此次会盟有何志向
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.68,0:27:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}刘备虽不才
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.08,0:27:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}却想以天下兴亡为已任
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.79,0:27:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}除贼安邦 中兴大汉
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.79,0:27:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.80,0:27:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那么如何才能实现你的雄心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.50,0:27:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}天下大乱之根源
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.10,0:28:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}首先在于人心丧乱
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.61,0:28:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}因此欲安天下 先取人心
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.18,0:28:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}而人心之本
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.68,0:28:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在于循天道 行仁义 持忠孝
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.89,0:28:17.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在下以为
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.89,0:28:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}如今安天下已经不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.49,0:28:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}取天下却有可能
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.89,0:28:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}而取天下之道在于权谋
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.30,0:28:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}权谋所至则英才毕集
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.10,0:28:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}上有贤君能臣 下有精兵强将
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.31,0:28:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}莫非曹将军暗怀君王之志吗
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.91,0:28:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}莫非你想取汉自立吗
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.18,0:28:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}曹某岂敢有这等非分之想
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.09,0:28:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不过 此次我一进城关
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.29,0:28:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就感觉到各路诸侯名为会盟
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.30,0:29:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}实则勾心斗角
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.50,0:29:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}暗藏雄心大志的也绝不在少数
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.20,0:29:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这一点在下也深有同感
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.01,0:29:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我一直在想 何以袁绍振臂一呼
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.11,0:29:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}十八路诸侯纷纷聚集会盟
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.88,0:29:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}难道他们真的想除贼扶汉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.39,0:29:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}未必
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.09,0:29:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}乱贼董卓原是西凉一刺史
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.29,0:29:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}其权位尚不如这些诸侯
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.10,0:29:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}而今呢
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.30,0:29:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}高踞京城 口衔天宪 独霸朝纲
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.10,0:29:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这就使得天下的众诸侯
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.81,0:29:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}心中不平啊
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.91,0:29:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他们会觉得昔日西凉一猪狗
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.51,0:29:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}怎配窃居龙廷
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.41,0:29:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}恕在下直言
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.58,0:29:58.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}与其说他们在仇恨董卓
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.99,0:30:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}倒不如说他们在嫉妒董卓
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.99,0:30:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}于是匆匆起兵 匆匆会盟
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.10,0:30:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}其意是想趁天下碎裂之时
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.20,0:30:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}争夺一块地盘
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.30,0:30:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}壮大自己的势力
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.80,0:30:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他们哪是在救天下
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.01,0:30:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他们是想趁乱争天下
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.91,0:30:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}趁乱分天下
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.31,0:30:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}所以在下才认定
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.32,0:30:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}天下大乱之根源
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.59,0:30:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}首先在于人心之丧乱
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.02,0:31:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}大哥 你跟刘备谈得如何啊
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.59,0:31:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你先说说
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.59,0:31:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你跟关羽张飞酒喝得如何
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.29,0:31:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好啊 关张这二位
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.70,0:31:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真是忠肝义胆豪气冲天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.40,0:31:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好 好 世上罕见的英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.70,0:31:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}如此英雄却不属于我
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.71,0:31:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}竟然落到了刘备手里
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.51,0:31:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}可惜 可叹 可恨哪
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.51,0:31:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}莫非 莫非刘备
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.72,0:31:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}没能让大哥收入靡下
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.89,0:31:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}此人既非囊中物 也非池中鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.89,0:31:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他暗藏雄心大志岂能为我所用
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.00,0:31:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但愿日后不要成为我的大敌才好
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.31,0:32:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.61,0:32:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}此次一战即攻下了白马要寨
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.12,0:32:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}足以可见西凉兵徒有虚名
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.02,0:32:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}父亲何不乘胜追击 拿下虎牢关
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.72,0:32:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}直接进入京师洛阳
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.19,0:32:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}只要我军率先进入
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.99,0:32:19.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}父亲就是首功
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.50,0:32:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我儿壮志可嘉呀
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.90,0:32:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}现在我军孤军深入数百里
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.01,0:32:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}已经远离了盟军大营
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.11,0:32:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}袁绍答应的粮草和援军
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.21,0:32:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}却一直不到
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.82,0:32:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}末将建议
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.02,0:32:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我军先做休整
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.02,0:32:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}待袁绍大军抵达之后
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.42,0:32:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}再共同进攻虎牢关
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.69,0:32:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}韩将军言之有理
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.60,0:32:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不过 等袁绍援兵抵达后
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.40,0:33:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我军仍然要承担先锋重任
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.10,0:33:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}因为此次剿贼
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.91,0:33:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}共有十八九路诸侯彼此争雄
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.41,0:33:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他们谁不想建功立业啊
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.61,0:33:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}谁不想率先攻入洛阳
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.61,0:33:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}以求天子封赏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.92,0:33:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}所以我江东子弟一定要为天下先
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.32,0:33:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在剿灭董卓之役中壮大实力
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.12,0:33:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}争得城池
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.32,0:33:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}以利日后发展
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.59,0:33:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}报
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.10,0:33:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}禀主公 董卓来使求见
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.60,0:33:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}董卓使者
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.20,0:33:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}也罢 听听他说什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.31,0:33:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}喏
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.01,0:33:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在下中常侍李儒 拜见孙将军
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.42,0:33:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}李儒啊 来此何意
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.29,0:34:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在下特来给孙将军道贺的
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.70,0:34:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}贺什么 贺我一战功成
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.10,0:34:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}打败了你们西凉军吗
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.51,0:34:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这只是其中之一贺
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.41,0:34:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这二贺嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.91,0:34:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}孙将军你更有可贺之处啊
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.52,0:34:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}洗耳恭听
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.02,0:34:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}董相有一爱女年当花季
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.02,0:34:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}尚未及笄
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.13,0:34:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}孙将军你有一爱子 名叫孙权
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.60,0:34:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}董相素来敬佩将军
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.40,0:34:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}想将爱女嫁与孙将军之子
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.60,0:34:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}结为儿女亲家
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.51,0:34:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}共图大业啊
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.81,0:34:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}嫁给我哪个儿子
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.01,0:34:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}孙权
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.51,0:34:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}董相还说了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.02,0:34:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}如果将军有美意
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.02,0:34:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}相国立刻呈报天子
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.12,0:35:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}授孙将军你为朝廷大司马
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.42,0:35:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}位居三公啊
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.43,0:35:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}而且 而且
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.63,0:35:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}让孙将军你领荆州刺史
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.70,0:35:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}统领荆州九郡所有的城池啊
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.01,0:35:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}叫权儿进来
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.31,0:35:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}请二公子入内
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.02,0:35:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}爹 权儿来了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.73,0:35:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}儿啊 来 过来 哎
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.30,0:35:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}儿啊 董卓派人来给你提亲了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.51,0:35:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他就是孙权
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.41,0:35:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}世人传闻孙权是文武超群
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.11,0:36:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}智勇双全
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.72,0:36:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他 他怎么还是个娃娃呀
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.12,0:36:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我儿个个智勇双全文武超群
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.43,0:36:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不信 咱可以问问他
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.13,0:36:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}儿啊 来
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.80,0:36:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}爹问问你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.91,0:36:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这位使者为什么要给你送个媳妇
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.11,0:36:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}董卓被我爹爹打怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.91,0:36:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}所以才让我做他的女婿
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.42,0:36:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这样爹爹就变成了他的奴才
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.72,0:36:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}爹
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.52,0:36:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这件事你可万万不能答应他呀
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.42,0:36:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}听见了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.22,0:36:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}连我九岁的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.53,0:36:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}都能看出董卓的祸心
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.93,0:36:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这等离间计还能瞒得过天下人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.44,0:36:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在下失言
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.60,0:36:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在下告罪
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.41,0:37:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}李儒啊 滚回去
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.11,0:37:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}告诉董卓
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.91,0:37:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}叫他洗干净脖子
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.82,0:37:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}等我的战刀
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.02,0:37:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}爹啊 刚才权儿又想了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.63,0:37:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你可以答应董卓
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.53,0:37:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.23,0:37:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.23,0:37:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}咱们不是真的答应而是假装答应
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.03,0:37:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}兵书上说兵不厌诈
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.13,0:37:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你假装答应以后 趁西凉军不备
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.50,0:37:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}领军突然杀进洛阳城
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.91,0:37:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}妙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.72,0:37:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}都听见了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.22,0:37:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我小小的儿子就如此多智
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.12,0:37:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}何愁江东大业不成
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.53,0:37:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}恭喜主公 贺喜主公
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.72,0:38:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}报
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.52,0:38:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}先锋将军孙坚传来第三道书信
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.63,0:38:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}急催粮饷和援军
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.93,0:38:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}知道了 叫袁术来见我
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.24,0:38:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}喏
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.94,0:38:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}报
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.71,0:38:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}禀盟主 孙坚遣将叩营
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.81,0:38:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}来将何人
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.51,0:38:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}上将黄盖
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.59,0:39:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}黄将军亲自来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.13,0:39:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}袁盟主请看
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.43,0:39:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}末将这把战剑
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.84,0:39:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}已经砍杀过二十五个西凉贼子
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.24,0:39:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}剑身已残 剑锋崩缺
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.44,0:39:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}此时此刻
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.64,0:39:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我数万江东子弟就像这把战剑
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.41,0:39:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}正在虎牢关下与西凉兵孤军血战
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.12,0:39:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}而你答应的粮饷 战马 军械
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.22,0:39:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}现在何处
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.02,0:39:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}黄将军莫急
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.82,0:39:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}粮饷军械我早已叫袁术
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.03,0:39:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}给孙将军送去了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.23,0:39:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}料想三五日之内必送到
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.13,0:39:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}还说三五日
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.94,0:39:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}如今几个三五日都过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.74,0:39:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我主公一不见粮饷
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.24,0:39:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}二不见军械 三不见援军
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.44,0:39:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}而我进关时却看见
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.91,0:39:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}众诸侯都在营中饮酒作乐
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.21,0:39:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}根本不见进军的迹象
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.42,0:39:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}哪里 哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.42,0:40:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}五镇诸侯已经率兵出关了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.83,0:40:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不日即可与孙将军会合
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.93,0:40:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这样吧 黄将军还是退下歇息
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.93,0:40:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}容我稍做布置
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.04,0:40:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不 禀盟主 我主公说了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.04,0:40:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不见粮草军械
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.44,0:40:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我就不离开盟主寸步
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.91,0:40:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}黄将军 日落之前
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.32,0:40:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我定将粮饷军械交付于你
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.22,0:40:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好 袁盟主一言为定 再不食言
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.82,0:40:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}一言为定 有如此剑
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.53,0:40:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}黄将军 还是退下歇息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.00,0:41:33.39,lrc,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}大梦方觉  山川依旧
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.39,0:41:45.12,lrc,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}古战场上  几度春秋
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.15,0:41:52.38,lrc,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}路没有头  情不能收
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.38,0:42:04.97,lrc,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}检点平生志未酬
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.97,0:42:17.13,lrc,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}青梅煮酒  要把话儿说透
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.13,0:42:28.57,lrc,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}天下英雄  谁是敌手
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.57,0:42:37.21,lrc,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}烈火飞舟  你必须回头
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.21,0:42:46.22,lrc,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}江东子弟也风流
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.22,0:42:52.86,lrc,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}不是空  也不是有
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.86,0:43:00.22,lrc,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}一缕英魂到永久
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.22,0:43:10.12,lrc,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}不是去  也不是留
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.12,0:43:18.08,lrc,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}往来在人间  与天地同寿
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.08,0:43:30.57,lrc,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}与天地同寿
